1. Nf3 d5 2. e4 dxe4 3. Ng5 Nf6 {Not a good move due to the reply Bc4 which 
forces Black to play e6.} 4. d3 (4. Bc4 $1) exd3 {Black should've considered} 
(4... Bg4) {here} 5. Bxd3 h6 $4 {The mistake} 6. Nxf7 {If Black moves the Queen 
White will pick up the rook with a continued brutal attack. However, if Black 
takes...} Kxf7 7. Bg6+ 1-0

