1. e4 d5 2. Nf3 dxe4 3. Ng5 Bf5 4. d3 {This leads nowhere.} exd3 5. Bxd3 {If} 
(5. Qf3 $2 dxc2 $1 6. Qxf5 $4 Qd1#) Bxd3 6. cxd3 h6 {Kicking back White's only 
active piece. Black is better due to being a pawn up and White's IQP on the 3rd 
rank. Also fine is} (6... Nf6) {After} (6... Nc6 7. Qb3) {is a bit annoying} *

