this is strongly met by...} e6 {Unleashing the attack on the undefended knight. 
Black should be prepared for the following sort of attempt.} 5. h4 h6 6. Qh5 Qd7 
{Or} (6... Bg6 7. Nxe6 Bxh5 8. Nxd8 Kxd8) 7. d4 Nf6 8. Qxf7+ Qxf7 9. Nxf7 Kxf7 *

